data.content:
noun
plural -dents
[count] a person who does not live in a particular town, city, state, or country :a person who is not a resident
Nonresidents need to fill out special paperwork to get a library card.
This parking lot is closed to nonresidents.
non-resident Brit :a person who is not staying in a particular hotel
The hotel dining room is open to non-residents for dinner.
